About

TECHCAMP Is a seedbed that seeks to guide and support digital talent from all regions of the country, where it attracts people with high potential in software development skills and who are starting their working life. The accompaniment process involves the construction of technological solutions for real challenges, so that the immersion in the seedbed meets the main objective..
